{"tid":189974,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀到就黎grad 先發現書好重要","createTime":"2017-04-06T22:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T13:37:43.000Z","uid":15249,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48809b70a91f64f3c965bf46117652abb9a71091","tid":189974,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:02:47.000Z","msg":"今年year4 發現個人好膚淺<br />\n雖然好多野都識小小咁 但其實都係一知半解<br />\n老左先發現 書到用時方恨少呢句野幾咁重要<br />\n亦都發現 以前誤解左呢句野<br />\n其實香港教學學到既野8成都係應試<br />\n最重要既知識少之又少<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n其實係想求大家介紹返幾本書小弟睇<br />\n古今中外都得 內容不限<br />\n最好易入口d既 培養返個閱讀習慣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9cd526084241216b9149311d210863ffc7374b","tid":189974,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:03:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Spirit_of_the_Chinese_People\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_Spirit_of_the_Chinese_People&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=96d481d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Spirit_of_the_Chinese_People</a>"},{"pid":"d05a162c0caab39dc52d2c89118d8bf2f0b2c183","tid":189974,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Spirit_of_the_Chinese_People\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_Spirit_of_the_Chinese_People&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=96d481d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Spirit_of_the_Chinese_People</a></blockquote><br />\nbookmark左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28db1395d558e1f3f093f66b4ab5ecaa4ee2816c","tid":189974,"uid":93430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:12:30.000Z","msg":"How to Read a Book by M. J. Adler"},{"pid":"74e9bd84644b5a19101